ActWestern Economic Diversification Act
SubjectAgreement with the Province of Alberta for the delivery of the Community Adjustment Fund.
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of the Western Economic Diversification, on behalf of the Government of Canada, to enter into a federal-provincial cost-shared agreement with the Province of Alberta for the purpose of delivering the Community Adjustment Fund (CAF). The agreement will be in effect for two years in accordance with the provisions of Budget 2009.
